methods.comment:
* Computes the frame type to invoke the target method handle with. This is the same as the * caller frame type, but with the trailing argument being the array type that is the * trailing argument in the target method handle. * *

Suppose the targetType is (T0, T1, T2[])RT and the callerType is (C0, C1, C2, C3)RC * then the constructed type is (C0, C1, T2[])RC.
